    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-120@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Create and manage a project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Opprett og håndter et prosjekt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-121@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A project pairs a source language with the locales you translate into, the files in scope, and the flows that process them. Naming it is the only required step — everything else is configured visually. The project home shows each content collection's translation status — how many blocks are covered per locale — and lets you extract content into the project store to refresh it."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et prosjekt parer et kildespråk med språkene du oversetter til, filene i omfang og flytene som behandler dem. Å navngi det er det eneste obligatoriske steget — alt annet konfigureres visuelt. Prosjekthjemmet viser oversettelsesstatusen for hver innholdssamling — hvor mange blokker som er dekket per språk — og lar deg trekke innhold ut i prosjektlageret for å friske den opp."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-122@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Manage content in a project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Håndter innhold i et prosjekt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-123@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A project's content is the set of files it translates. Glob patterns are grouped into named collections — documentation, store UI, contracts, templates — each mapping source files to their translated counterparts. The Content view shows the patterns alongside the real files they match and the format Kapi detected for each."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et prosjekts innhold er settet av filer det oversetter. Globmønstre grupperes i navngitte samlinger — dokumentasjon, butikkgrensesnitt, kontrakter, maler — som hver kartlegger kildefiler til sine oversatte motstykker. Innholdsvisningen viser mønstrene side om side med de virkelige filene de treffer og formatet Kapi oppdaget for hver av dem."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-124@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Compose flows"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Sett sammen flyter"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-125@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A project's flows are the pipelines it runs over its content — a plain AI translation, a translation followed by quality checks, a pseudo-translation for testing. Each flow is a named sequence of steps, saved alongside the project and shared through version control. Open one to see and edit its pipeline."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et prosjekts flyter er pipelinene det kjører over innholdet sitt — en ren AI-oversettelse, en oversettelse fulgt av kvalitetskontroller, en pseudooversettelse for testing. Hver flyt er en navngitt sekvens av steg, lagret sammen med prosjektet og delt gjennom versjonskontroll. Åpne en for å se og redigere pipelinen dens."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-126@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Configure appearance, providers, and plugins"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Konfigurer utseende, leverandører og tillegg"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-127@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Settings gather everything in one place: light or dark appearance, the AI providers Kapi translates with (keys stay in your OS keychain), and the plugins that extend its formats and tools."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Innstillinger samler alt på ett sted: lyst eller mørkt utseende, AI-leverandørene Kapi oversetter med (nøklene blir i operativsystemets nøkkelring), og tilleggene som utvider formatene og verktøyene."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-128@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Browse terminology and translation memory"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Bla i terminologi og oversettelsesminne"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-129@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi keeps a glossary of multi-locale terms and a memory of past translations. Both are searchable, with inline formatting and entity placeholders preserved."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi holder en ordliste med termer på flere språk og et minne over tidligere oversettelser. Begge er søkbare, med inline-formatering og entitetsplassholdere bevart."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-12@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "There are two ways to drive Kapi:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Det er to måter å bruke Kapi på:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-130@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Using the Okapi plugin"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Bruke Okapi-tillegget"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-131@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Plugins extend Kapi with new formats and tools. The Okapi bridge adds the [Okapi Framework](https://okapiframework.org/)'s filters — dozens of document formats beyond the built-in set. Install it from the registry in one click, and projects built on those filters, like the OkapiMart sample, open and process their files through them."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Tillegg utvider Kapi med nye formater og verktøy. Okapi-broen legger til filtrene fra [Okapi Framework](https://okapiframework.org/) — dusinvis av dokumentformater utover det innebygde settet. Installer det fra registeret med ett klikk, og prosjekter bygget på de filtrene, som OkapiMart-eksempelet, åpner og behandler filene sine gjennom dem."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-132@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Features"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Funksjoner"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-133@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Project dashboard** — Open to your projects and pick up where you left off. Each project home shows its languages, content collections, and per-locale translation status, with flows a click from running."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Prosjektoversikt** — Åpne til prosjektene dine og fortsett der du slapp. Hvert prosjekthjem viser språkene, innholdssamlingene og oversettelsesstatusen per språk, med flytene ett klikk fra å kjøre."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-134@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Flow editor** — Build multi-tool pipelines visually. Chain AI translation, quality checks, pseudo-translation, and more into reusable flows saved in the project."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Flytredigering** — Bygg pipeliner med flere verktøy visuelt. Lenk AI-oversettelse, kvalitetskontroller, pseudooversettelse og mer sammen i gjenbrukbare flyter lagret i prosjektet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-135@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Flow runner** — Execute a project's flows with live progress visualization: per-file status, node highlighting, and timing. Runs use the recipe's languages and content, so there are no flags to repeat."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Flytkjøring** — Utfør et prosjekts flyter med direkte fremdriftsvisning: status per fil, nodeutheving og tidsbruk. Kjøringer bruker oppskriftens språk og innhold, så det er ingen flagg å gjenta."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-136@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Quick tools (ad-hoc)** — For one-offs, run an individual tool or flow on a loose file with dynamic configuration forms generated from tool schemas — no project required."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Hurtigverktøy (ad hoc)** — For engangstilfeller, kjør et enkeltverktøy eller en flyt på en løs fil med dynamiske konfigurasjonsskjemaer generert fra verktøyskjemaene — ikke noe prosjekt kreves."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-137@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Plugin manager** — Browse the plugin registry, install, update, and manage plugins from a UI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Tilleggshåndtering** — Bla i tilleggsregisteret, installer, oppdater og håndter tillegg fra et grensesnitt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-138@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Credential vault** — Store AI provider API keys securely in your OS keychain."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Legitimasjonshvelv** — Lagre API-nøkler for AI-leverandører trygt i operativsystemets nøkkelring."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-139@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Project files** — The `.kapi` recipe is a portable file you can share via git or open with double-click."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Prosjektfiler** — `.kapi`-oppskriften er en portabel fil du kan dele via git eller åpne med et dobbeltklikk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-13@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Project** — the recommended day-to-day model. Capture the workflow once in a portable `.kapi` recipe (languages, content patterns, flows, plugin requirements, defaults) and replay it with `kapi run <flow>`. The project store accumulates translation memory as you work, and the recipe is shareable via git. Best for any repository or content set you localize repeatedly — [create your first project](/kapi/get-started/first-project)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Prosjekt** — den anbefalte modellen for daglig bruk. Fang arbeidsflyten én gang i en portabel `.kapi`-oppskrift (språk, innholdsmønstre, flyter, tilleggskrav, standardvalg) og spill den av igjen med `kapi run <flow>`. Prosjektlageret bygger opp oversettelsesminne mens du arbeider, og oppskriften kan deles via git. Best for ethvert kodelager eller innholdssett du lokaliserer gjentatte ganger — [opprett ditt første prosjekt](/kapi/get-started/first-project)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-140@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "On macOS, the cask installs the app and bundles the `kapi` CLI:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "På macOS installerer casken appen og inkluderer `kapi`-CLI-en:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-141@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "For the Windows installer and the macOS DMG / Linux tarball builds, see [Installation](/kapi/get-started/installation#install-kapi-desktop)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "For Windows-installasjonsprogrammet og macOS-DMG-/Linux-tarball-byggene, se [Installering](/kapi/get-started/installation#installer-kapi-desktop)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-142@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Your first project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ditt første prosjekt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-143@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The tour above shows each surface in motion; here is the path through them when you start from nothing. Everything is configured visually — there is no YAML to write by hand."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Omvisningen over viser hver flate i bevegelse; her er veien gjennom dem når du starter fra ingenting. Alt konfigureres visuelt — det er ingen YAML å skrive for hånd."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-144@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Create the project.** Launch Kapi Desktop and click **New Project**. Give it a name, set the **source language** (e.g. `en-US`), and add the **target languages** you translate into (e.g. `fr-FR`, `de-DE`). Naming it is the only required step."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Opprett prosjektet.** Start Kapi Desktop og klikk **New Project**. Gi det et navn, sett **kildespråket** (f.eks. `en-US`), og legg til **målspråkene** du oversetter til (f.eks. `fr-FR`, `de-DE`). Å navngi det er det eneste obligatoriske steget."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-145@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Add content.** In the **Content** view, add a pattern that points at your source files — for example `src/locales/en/*.json`. Kapi lists the files it matches and the format it detected for each, grouped into a named collection."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Legg til innhold.** I **Content**-visningen, legg til et mønster som peker på kildefilene dine — for eksempel `src/locales/en/*.json`. Kapi lister filene det treffer og formatet den oppdaget for hver av dem, gruppert i en navngitt samling."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-146@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Add a provider key.** In **Settings → Providers** (or **Credentials**), add an AI provider and paste your API key. Keys are stored in your OS keychain, never in the project file."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Legg til en leverandørnøkkel.** I **Settings → Providers** (eller **Credentials**), legg til en AI-leverandør og lim inn API-nøkkelen din. Nøkler lagres i operativsystemets nøkkelring, aldri i prosjektfilen."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-147@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Compose a flow.** In **Flows**, create a flow and add the steps you need — an AI translation, optionally followed by a quality or terminology check. Each flow is a named pipeline saved alongside the project."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Sett sammen en flyt.** I **Flows**, opprett en flyt og legg til stegene du trenger — en AI-oversettelse, eventuelt fulgt av en kvalitets- eller terminologikontroll. Hver flyt er en navngitt pipeline lagret sammen med prosjektet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-148@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Run it.** Select the flow, pick input files and a target language, and click **Run**. You'll see per-file progress, node highlighting, timing, and the output file locations."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Kjør den.** Velg flyten, velg inndatafiler og et målspråk, og klikk **Run**. Du ser fremdrift per fil, nodeutheving, tidsbruk og plasseringen av utdatafilene."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-149@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Install plugins (optional).** In **Plugins**, browse the registry and install the **Okapi Bridge** to add its document formats and filters; new formats appear automatically."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Installer tillegg (valgfritt).** I **Plugins**, bla i registeret og installer **Okapi Bridge** for å legge til dokumentformatene og filtrene dens; nye formater dukker opp automatisk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-14@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad-hoc** — run a tool or flow directly on files, configured by flags (or, in the desktop app, clicks): `kapi ai-translate -i file.json --target-lang fr`. Nothing is saved — the quick path for one-off jobs, scripting, and CI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad hoc** — kjør et verktøy eller en flyt direkte på filer, konfigurert med flagg (eller, i skrivebordsappen, med klikk): `kapi ai-translate -i file.json --target-lang fr`. Ingenting lagres — den raske veien for engangsjobber, skripting og CI."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-150@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Everything you configure is written to a portable `<name>.kapi` recipe file. Commit it to git to share with your team, reopen it in Kapi Desktop, or run it from the command line:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Alt du konfigurerer skrives til en portabel `<name>.kapi`-oppskriftsfil. Sjekk den inn i git for å dele med laget ditt, gjenåpne den i Kapi Desktop, eller kjør den fra kommandolinjen:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
