    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-255@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Using kapi with Claude"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Bruke kapi med Claude"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-256@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "You keep building with Claude Code as usual. kapi gives Claude a **structured, repeatable** way to handle localization and brand — so making your product multilingual and keeping its copy on-voice is an engineering pipeline, not a one-off translation. kapi extracts the text from your **code** and **documents**, round-trips it back **faithfully** (structure, formatting, and placeholders intact), reuses **translation memory**, and enforces your **glossary** and **brand voice** — the same way every time, and gate-able in CI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Du fortsetter å bygge med Claude Code som vanlig. kapi gir Claude en **strukturert, repeterbar** måte å håndtere lokalisering og merkevare på — slik at det å gjøre produktet ditt flerspråklig og holde teksten på stemmen er en ingeniørpipeline, ikke en engangsoversettelse. kapi trekker teksten ut av **koden** og **dokumentene** dine, fører den tilbake **formattro** (struktur, formatering og plassholdere intakt), gjenbruker **oversettelsesminne**, og håndhever **ordlisten** og **merkevarestemmen** din — på samme måte hver gang, og kan brukes som port i CI."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-257@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "You install it once. After that you ask Claude in plain language; it decides when to call `kapi`."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Du installerer det én gang. Etter det spør du Claude i naturlig språk; den avgjør når den skal kalle `kapi`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-258@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": ":::note kapi also speaks [MCP](/reference/mcp), for assistants that prefer structured tools over a CLI. This page follows the skill (CLI) path — the two work together. :::"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": ":::note kapi snakker også [MCP](/reference/mcp), for assistenter som foretrekker strukturerte verktøy fremfor en CLI. Denne siden følger ferdighetssporet (CLI) — de to virker sammen. :::"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-259@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "1. Plug kapi into Claude"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "1. Koble kapi til Claude"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-25@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The bright line: **bilingual round-trip and asset interchange both hand a file to a counterpart and bring the result back, with project state holding the way back; format conversion is one-way.** This page is the bilingual round-trip — the handoff to a translator or TMS."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Den klare linjen: **tospråklig rundtur og ressursutveksling leverer begge en fil til en motpart og henter resultatet tilbake, med prosjekttilstand som holder veien tilbake; formatkonvertering er énveis.** Denne siden er den tospråklige rundturen — overleveringen til en oversetter eller et TMS."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-260@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Install the skill into a project, or into your user account for every project:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Installer ferdigheten i et prosjekt, eller i brukerkontoen din for alle prosjekter:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-261@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Claude Code discovers the skill and invokes it when a task fits its description — you never call it by name. It's one router that loads the relevant section on demand (progressive disclosure), so it covers the whole workflow without crowding the context window."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Claude Code oppdager ferdigheten og kaller den når en oppgave passer beskrivelsen dens — du kaller den aldri ved navn. Det er én ruter som laster den relevante seksjonen ved behov (progressiv avsløring), så den dekker hele arbeidsflyten uten å fylle opp kontekstvinduet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-262@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The only prerequisite is the `kapi` CLI on your `PATH` (`kapi version` — see [installation](/kapi/get-started/installation)). The rule-based checks need no credential; for provider-backed translation, add one with `kapi credentials add` (or let the assistant translate within kapi's guardrails — more below)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Den eneste forutsetningen er `kapi`-CLI-en på `PATH` (`kapi version` — se [installering](/kapi/get-started/installation)). De regelbaserte sjekkene trenger ingen legitimasjon; for leverandørstøttet oversettelse, legg til en med `kapi credentials add` (eller la assistenten oversette innenfor kapis rekkverk — mer under)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-263@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "2. Ship your app in another language"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "2. Lever appen din på et annet språk"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-264@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "You're taking a React or Next.js app to a new market. The English text in your JSX stays as it is — no message IDs, no `t(\"...\")` wrappers. You just ask:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Du tar en React- eller Next.js-app til et nytt marked. Den engelske teksten i JSX-en din blir som den er — ingen meldings-ID-er, ingen `t(\"...\")`-innpakninger. Du bare spør:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-265@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "We're launching in Japan. Set up i18n with kapi-react and add a Japanese translation."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Vi lanserer i Japan. Sett opp i18n med kapi-react og legg til en japansk oversettelse."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-266@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Claude adopts the zero-wrapper [kapi-react](/react/introduction) stack and runs a structured pipeline — the same steps every time the UI changes:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Claude tar i bruk null-innpaknings-stabelen [kapi-react](/react/introduction) og kjører en strukturert pipeline — de samme stegene hver gang grensesnittet endres:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-267@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The strings stay in your components as plain JSX; kapi handles the build-time extraction and the round-trip into a runtime dictionary, carrying placeholders like `{userName}` through untouched. The note *data* in your components is left alone — only the UI copy is translated. Add the next locale by re-running the same pipeline."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Strengene blir i komponentene dine som ren JSX; kapi håndterer uttrekket ved byggetid og rundturen inn i en kjøretidsordbok, og bærer plassholdere som `{userName}` urørt gjennom. Notat-*dataene* i komponentene dine får være i fred — bare grensesnittsteksten oversettes. Legg til neste språk ved å kjøre samme pipeline på nytt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-268@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "3. Translate documents, structure intact"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "3. Oversett dokumenter med strukturen intakt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-269@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Next, a launch one-pager — a Word document. Claude drives kapi for a structured, format-faithful round-trip: kapi parses the `.docx`, translates the text, and writes it back with the headings, lists, bold runs, and inline fields preserved — applying your glossary and translation memory along the way."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Deretter, en énsider for lanseringen — et Word-dokument. Claude driver kapi for en strukturert, formattro rundtur: kapi parser `.docx`-en, oversetter teksten og skriver den tilbake med overskrifter, lister, fete tekstløp og innebygde felter bevart — og anvender ordlisten og oversettelsesminnet ditt underveis."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-26@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Two carriers, chosen by recipient.** neokapi's native interchange format is the lossless **bilingual `.klz`** (`kapi extract --format klz`) — for a translator or reviewer working in kapi or the neokapi review tool; it carries inline codes, TM matches, and term context in one file and gives integrity-verified, diffable review. For a recipient on a third-party CAT tool, `kapi extract` emits **XLIFF 2.x / PO** (the default), the industry-interop tier this page focuses on. Both go out and come back through the same `extract` / `merge` verbs. See [KLF vs XLIFF](/reference/klf/vs-xliff)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**To bærere, valgt etter mottaker.** neokapis egne utvekslingsformat er den tapsfrie **tospråklige `.klz`-en** (`kapi extract --format klz`) — for en oversetter eller korrekturleser som arbeider i kapi eller neokapis gjennomgangsverktøy; den bærer inline-koder, TM-treff og termkontekst i én fil og gir integritetsverifisert, diff-bar gjennomgang. For en mottaker på et tredjeparts CAT-verktøy skriver `kapi extract` ut **XLIFF 2.x / PO** (standard), bransjeinterop-nivået denne siden fokuserer på. Begge går ut og kommer tilbake gjennom de samme verbene `extract` / `merge`. Se [KLF vs XLIFF](/reference/klf/vs-xliff)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-270@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Translate announcement.docx into Japanese."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oversett announcement.docx til japansk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-271@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi CLI recipes"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi CLI-oppskrifter"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-272@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Each recipe takes a single task — estimate a job, catch UI truncation, enforce a glossary — states the goal, walks the steps, and lets you run the commands yourself. The interactive embeds run the real `kapi` binary in your browser: no install, no server, no API key. Every command shown is the command that runs."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver oppskrift tar én enkelt oppgave — anslå en jobb, fange opp avkutting i grensesnittet, håndheve en ordliste — angir målet, går gjennom stegene og lar deg kjøre kommandoene selv. De interaktive innbyggingene kjører den ekte `kapi`-binærfilen i nettleseren din: ingen installasjon, ingen server, ingen API-nøkkel. Hver kommando som vises er kommandoen som kjører."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-273@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "For what kapi is and how the CLI and Kapi Desktop relate, see the [Kapi overview](/kapi/overview). For every command and flag, see the [command reference](/commands)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "For hva kapi er og hvordan CLI-en og Kapi Desktop henger sammen, se [Kapi-oversikten](/kapi/overview). For hver kommando og hvert flagg, se [kommandoreferansen](/commands)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-274@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc or project?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ad hoc eller prosjekt?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-275@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A **`.kapi` project is the recommended working model** for any repository or content set you localize repeatedly. It captures the languages, content patterns, and flows in a committed recipe once, adds git-style upward discovery of that recipe from any subdirectory, and keeps a project-local translation memory and termbase that every run reuses — so you stop repeating flags and start accumulating work. [Create your first project](/kapi/get-started/first-project) walks the setup; the [project file reference](/reference/project-file) covers the recipe format and discovery rules."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et **`.kapi`-prosjekt er den anbefalte arbeidsmodellen** for ethvert kodelager eller innholdssett du lokaliserer gjentatte ganger. Det fanger språkene, innholdsmønstrene og flytene i en innsjekket oppskrift én gang, legger til git-aktig oppdagelse av oppskriften oppover fra enhver underkatalog, og holder et prosjektlokalt oversettelsesminne og en termbase som hver kjøring gjenbruker — slik at du slutter å gjenta flagg og begynner å bygge opp arbeid. [Opprett ditt første prosjekt](/kapi/get-started/first-project) går gjennom oppsettet; [referansen for prosjektfiler](/reference/project-file) dekker oppskriftsformatet og oppdagelsesreglene."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-276@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "kapi also runs **ad-hoc**: a command operates directly on the files you name, configured by flags, with nothing saved — `kapi ai-translate -i messages.json --target-lang fr`. That's the quick path for one-off jobs, scripting, and CI, and a fine on-ramp. Many recipes here are shown ad-hoc because they're genuine one-offs; each notes the project-mode equivalent where it helps."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "kapi kjører også **ad hoc**: en kommando arbeider direkte på filene du navngir, konfigurert med flagg, uten at noe lagres — `kapi ai-translate -i messages.json --target-lang fr`. Det er den raske veien for engangsjobber, skripting og CI, og en fin innkjøring. Mange oppskrifter her vises ad hoc fordi de er genuine engangstilfeller; hver av dem nevner prosjektmodus-ekvivalenten der det hjelper."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-277@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Every recipe is marked at the top with its mode — **Runs anywhere** (ad-hoc) or **Needs a `.kapi` project**."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver oppskrift er merket øverst med modusen sin — **Kjører hvor som helst** (ad hoc) eller **Krever et `.kapi`-prosjekt**."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
