    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-4@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**[Kapi Desktop](/kapi/desktop/overview)** — a visual companion app for building flows, running tools, managing plugins, and storing AI credentials — without writing YAML or remembering flags."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**[Kapi Desktop](/kapi/desktop/overview)** — en visuell følgeapp for å bygge flyter, kjøre verktøy, håndtere tillegg og lagre AI-legitimasjon — uten å skrive YAML eller huske flagg."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-50@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Common extract options"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Vanlige uttrekksvalg"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-51@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Multi-target in one pass is the default. Omit `--target-lang` to use every locale in `defaults.target_languages`; pass a comma-separated subset to restrict."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flere mål i én omgang er standard. Utelat `--target-lang` for å bruke hvert språk i `defaults.target_languages`; send en kommaseparert delmengde for å begrense."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-52@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "When extraction is redacted (`--redact`, `--redact-rules`, or `defaults.redaction` in the recipe), the emitted file carries only placeholders and the originals stay in a local vault; `kapi merge` restores them automatically. See [Redaction](/framework/redaction)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når uttrekket er sladdet (`--redact`, `--redact-rules`, eller `defaults.redaction` i oppskriften), bærer den utskrevne filen bare plassholdere og originalene blir i et lokalt hvelv; `kapi merge` gjenoppretter dem automatisk. Se [Sladding](/framework/redaction)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-53@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Day 2: translator work"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dag 2: oversetterarbeid"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-54@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Out-of-scope for kapi. The translator opens the XLIFF/PO in their CAT tool of choice, translates it, and returns it. Kapi is entirely out of the loop during this phase — which is exactly the point. Any bilingual tool that speaks XLIFF 2.x works."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Utenfor kapis ansvar. Oversetteren åpner XLIFF-en/PO-en i sitt foretrukne CAT-verktøy, oversetter den og returnerer den. Kapi er helt ute av sløyfen i denne fasen — som er nettopp poenget. Ethvert tospråklig verktøy som snakker XLIFF 2.x fungerer."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-55@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Day N: merge the return"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dag N: flett inn returen"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-56@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Merge resolves the extraction manifest by reading the batch id from the file's `<note category=\"kapi\" id=\"batch-id\">` — the filename can change during the vendor round-trip and merge still finds the right batch."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flettingen finner uttrekksmanifestet ved å lese batch-id-en fra filens `<note category=\"kapi\" id=\"batch-id\">` — filnavnet kan endre seg under leverandør-rundturen, og flettingen finner fortsatt riktig batch."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-57@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Multi-file in one pass:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flere filer i én omgang:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-58@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Each returning XLIFF is applied independently. A failure on one input (parse error, missing manifest, stale source) doesn't abort the others — per-file outcomes are reported and the exit code reflects any failure."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver returnerende XLIFF behandles uavhengig. En feil på én inndatafil (parsefeil, manglende manifest, foreldet kilde) avbryter ikke de andre — utfallet rapporteres per fil, og avslutningskoden gjenspeiler enhver feil."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-59@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Stale segments"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Foreldede segmenter"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-5@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Because both front-ends run the same engine, a workflow built in one works in the other: the flows and the project file are identical."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Siden begge grensesnittene kjører samme motor, fungerer en arbeidsflyt bygget i det ene også i det andre: flytene og prosjektfilen er identiske."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-60@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Merge compares every incoming block's `<source>` against the current source file. If the source text drifted since extract (someone edited the JSON while the XLIFF was out with the translator), that block is reported as **stale** and **skipped** — neither applied nor TM-absorbed. You can re-extract and re-translate the drifted portion."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flettingen sammenligner hver innkommende blokks `<source>` med den gjeldende kildefilen. Hvis kildeteksten har endret seg siden uttrekket (noen redigerte JSON-en mens XLIFF-en var ute hos oversetteren), rapporteres den blokken som **foreldet** og **hoppes over** — verken anvendt eller absorbert i oversettelsesminnet. Du kan trekke ut og oversette den endrede delen på nytt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-61@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Conflict policy"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Konfliktpolicy"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-62@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "When an on-disk target (or TM TU) already carries a translation for a block, `merge.conflict_policy` picks what happens:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når et mål på disk (eller en TU i oversettelsesminnet) allerede bærer en oversettelse for en blokk, velger `merge.conflict_policy` hva som skjer:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-63@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The same policy applies to TM write-back when a TU for this source already has a translation — never ambiguous, never interactive."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Samme policy gjelder for TM-tilbakeskriving når en TU for denne kilden allerede har en oversettelse — aldri tvetydig, aldri interaktiv."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-64@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Audit: what did this merge contribute?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Revisjon: hva bidro denne flettingen med?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-65@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Lists every TM entry written or updated by a specific merge with timestamp, source file path, block content hash, and originating XLIFF filename — the answer to \"what did this merge do?\" without leaving the CLI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Lister hver TM-oppføring skrevet eller oppdatert av en bestemt fletting, med tidsstempel, kildefilsti, blokkens innholdshash og opprinnelig XLIFF-filnavn — svaret på «hva gjorde denne flettingen?» uten å forlate CLI-en."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-66@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "PO (gettext) alternative"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "PO-alternativet (gettext)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
