    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-69@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "File-level (on the header entry): `#. kapi-batch:`, `#. kapi-source-file:`, `#. kapi-source-hash:`"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "På filnivå (på hodeoppføringen): `#. kapi-batch:`, `#. kapi-source-file:`, `#. kapi-source-hash:`"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-6@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Extract content from a file, translate it, run checks, and write it back in the same format — a full bilingual round-trip from the terminal:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Trekk ut innhold fra en fil, oversett det, kjør sjekker og skriv det tilbake i samme format — en fullstendig tospråklig rundtur fra terminalen:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-70@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Per-entry: `#. kapi-block: <block-id>` for merge correlation"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Per oppføring: `#. kapi-block: <block-id>` for flettekorrelasjon"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-71@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "`#, fuzzy` on entries pre-filled from fuzzy TM matches"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "`#, fuzzy` på oppføringer forhåndsutfylt fra fuzzy TM-treff"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-72@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A single `kapi merge -i` invocation can mix XLIFF and PO inputs from the same batch — useful when different vendors ship in different formats."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ett enkelt `kapi merge -i`-kall kan blande XLIFF- og PO-inndata fra samme batch — nyttig når ulike leverandører leverer i ulike formater."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-73@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": ":::note PO output is one entry per block (matches the segmentation-off case). Enabling `defaults.segmentation.source: true` together with `--format po` errors early; emit XLIFF for projects that rely on sentence-level segmentation. :::"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": ":::note PO-utdata er én oppføring per blokk (tilsvarer tilfellet med segmentering av). Å slå på `defaults.segmentation.source: true` sammen med `--format po` feiler tidlig; skriv ut XLIFF for prosjekter som er avhengige av segmentering på setningsnivå. :::"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-74@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "What stays in the project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hva som blir i prosjektet"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-75@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "XLIFF and PO carry exactly one chosen target per locale, the source runs and inline codes, and — with the captured skeleton — enough to rebuild the original file byte-for-byte. Everything else in kapi's content model is **deliberately not** projected into the bilingual file; it stays in project state (the translation memory, termbase, and stand-off overlays):"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "XLIFF og PO bærer nøyaktig ett valgt mål per språk, kildens runs og inline-kodene, og — med det fangede skjelettet — nok til å gjenoppbygge originalfilen byte for byte. Alt annet i kapis innholdsmodell projiseres **bevisst ikke** inn i den tospråklige filen; det blir i prosjekttilstanden (oversettelsesminnet, termbasen og de frittstående overleggene):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-76@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Stand-off overlays** — terminology, entity, and QA annotations anchored to run ranges."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Frittstående overlegg** — terminologi-, entitets- og QA-annotasjoner forankret til run-områder."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-77@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Tone / channel variants** — alternate targets keyed by more than locale."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Tone-/kanalvarianter** — alternative mål nøklet på mer enn språkkode."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-78@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Provenance and status** — where each target came from (TM pre-fill, a specific merge batch, an MT or AI tool) and its review state."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Proveniens og status** — hvor hvert mål kom fra (TM-forhåndsutfylling, en bestemt flettebatch, et MT- eller AI-verktøy) og dets gjennomgangsstatus."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-79@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "This is by design: the bilingual file is the lean, tool-neutral handoff, and the project is the system of record. It is also why merge needs the same project the extract ran in — the skeleton and manifest that make the round-trip byte-exact live there, not in the file the translator returns."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dette er tilsiktet: den tospråklige filen er den slanke, verktøynøytrale overleveringen, og prosjektet er den autoritative kilden. Det er også derfor flettingen trenger det samme prosjektet uttrekket kjørte i — skjelettet og manifestet som gjør rundturen byte-eksakt bor der, ikke i filen oversetteren returnerer."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-7@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Command-line interface"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kommandolinjegrensesnitt"
          }
        ]
      },
