    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-84@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "[AD-013: Kapi CLI](/contribute/architecture/013-kapi-cli) — command tree and auto-discovery semantics"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "[AD-013: Kapi CLI](/contribute/architecture/013-kapi-cli) — kommandotreet og semantikken for automatisk oppdagelse"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-85@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "How Kapi runs: modes & bindings"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Slik kjører Kapi: moduser og bindinger"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-86@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi doesn't have separate \"ad-hoc commands\" and \"project commands.\" It has **one set of commands**, and what changes is the **binding** — where content comes from and where results go. Understanding that one idea makes every workflow below click."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi har ikke separate «ad hoc-kommandoer» og «prosjektkommandoer». Den har **ett sett med kommandoer**, og det som endres er **bindingen** — hvor innholdet kommer fra og hvor resultatene går. Forstår du den ene ideen, faller hver arbeidsflyt nedenfor på plass."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-87@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Two ways to run"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "To måter å kjøre på"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-88@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi runs the **same commands** two ways — the only difference is whether state is kept:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi kjører de **samme kommandoene** på to måter — den eneste forskjellen er om tilstand beholdes:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-89@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad-hoc** — run a tool or flow directly on files; nothing is saved."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad hoc** — kjør et verktøy eller en flyt direkte på filer; ingenting lagres."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-8@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Run tools and flows straight from the terminal — `kapi pseudo-translate`, `kapi ai-translate`, `kapi brand check`, `kapi run <flow>`. See the [Kapi CLI overview](/kapi/cli) for the command surface and the task-by-task recipes you can run in the browser."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kjør verktøy og flyter rett fra terminalen — `kapi pseudo-translate`, `kapi ai-translate`, `kapi brand check`, `kapi run <flow>`. Se [Kapi CLI-oversikten](/kapi/cli) for kommandoflaten og de oppgavebaserte oppskriftene du kan kjøre i nettleseren."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-90@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Project** — capture the workflow once in a portable `.kapi` recipe (languages, content patterns, flows, defaults) plus a `.kapi/` state directory that accumulates translation memory and per-block work."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Prosjekt** — fang arbeidsflyten én gang i en portabel `.kapi`-oppskrift (språk, innholdsmønstre, flyter, standardvalg) pluss en `.kapi/`-tilstandskatalog som bygger opp oversettelsesminne og arbeid per blokk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-91@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A **`.klz` parcel** moves work between the two: `pack` a project into a single file (or `extract` loose files into one), then `merge`/`unpack` on the other side."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En **`.klz`-pakke** flytter arbeid mellom de to: `pack` et prosjekt til én enkelt fil (eller `extract` løse filer til én), og deretter `merge`/`unpack` på den andre siden."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-92@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The binding model: source → flow → sink"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Bindingsmodellen: kilde → flyt → sluk"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-93@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A **flow** is just an ordered set of tools — it owns no input or output. Where the content enters (the **source**) and where results go (the **sink**) are *bindings* resolved when you run it:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En **flyt** er bare en ordnet rekke verktøy — den eier verken inndata eller utdata. Hvor innholdet kommer inn (**kilden**) og hvor resultatene går (**sluket**) er *bindinger* som løses når du kjører den:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-94@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The mode you're in is just which binding gets resolved:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Modusen du er i, er bare hvilken binding som blir løst:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-95@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad-hoc** = the `file` binding — you name `-i`/`-o`."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad hoc** = `file`-bindingen — du angir `-i`/`-o`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-96@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**In a project**, the default *sink* becomes the **store** (a *process-only* run); pass `-o` to force a file instead."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**I et prosjekt** blir standard-*sluket* **lageret** (en kjøring med *ren prosessering*); send `-o` for å tvinge en fil i stedet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-97@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Run `kapi run <flow> --explain` any time to print the resolved `source → sink` without executing:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kjør `kapi run <flow> --explain` når som helst for å skrive ut den løste `source → sink`-bindingen uten å kjøre:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-98@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc: loose files"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ad hoc: løse filer"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781160429293846857"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-99@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Project: two loops, both ending at `merge`"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Prosjekt: to sløyfer som begge ender i `merge`"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T06:47:09Z",
